        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Plan to contact your utility providers at least one to two weeks before your closing date. For New Braunfels Utilities, you can schedule service activation to coincide with your closing day so that electric and water are ready when you get the keys. Internet installation may require a longer lead time, especially if a technician visit is needed. Trash and recycling service through the City of New Braunfels is typically tied to the property address and may transfer automatically, but it is worth confirming. Your REALTOR can provide a checklist of everything you need to set up before move-in day."
        }
      }
    ]
  }
  </script>

  <ContactForm context="I'm relocating to New Braunfels and need help getting set up..." />
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .sub-hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 280px;
    background: url('/images/generated/hill-country-home-1.png') center/cover no-repeat;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .sub-hero__overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.55);
  }

  .sub-hero__content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .sub-hero__content h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .sub-hero__content p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  }

  .breadcrumb a {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .breadcrumb a:hover { color: #FF1616; }
  .breadcrumb span { margin: 0 0.3rem; }

  .page-intro {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--gray);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 800px;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .utility-groups {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .utility-group {
    background: #fafafa;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .utility-group__header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #FF1616;
  }

  .utility-group__header h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .utility-item {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
  }

  .utility-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

